comments: Jones (MEM) briefly places his hand on Thompson's (GSW) body as he enters his shooting motion and then immediately removes it. The marginal contact does not affect Thompson's jump shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) slightly extends his hand into Payton II's (GSW) back as he disengages from the pick and the marginal contact does not affect Payton II's ability to defend.

Wiggins (GSW) is in a legal guarding position when he absorbs the oncoming body contact from Morant (MEM) during his driving shot attempt. After absorbing the initial contact, Wiggins swipes down and avoids making contact to Morant's arm.
Payton II (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during Morant's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Payton II (GSW) slightly extends his forearm into Jones (MEM) as he turns and disengages from the pick. The contact is marginal.
Porter Jr. (GSW) reaches in and makes contact with the ball which dislodges it from Jackson Jr. (MEM) during the rebound. The contact to Jackson Jr's arm that follows is incidental.
As Jones (MEM) moves slightly into Wiggins (GSW) path during his dribble, Wiggins' momentum carries him into Jones' body and the contact affects his SQBR.
Clarke (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Payton II (GSW) and absorbs the contact from Payton II on the screen.
Wiggins (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and he makes contact to Morant's (MEM) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in a legal position in Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs during the off ball screen.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) reaches in makes marginal contact to Jones' (MEM) leg as he gathers the pass.
Payton II (GSW) reaches in and makes contact with the ball which dislodges it from Jones (MEM) during his dribble.
